Unique frame ID: #Z03 

♥ About Photo Frame ♥
Personalized photo frame. Made from acrylic glass. Includes your own custom photo and there is the option of different frame designs. The stylish look suits both modern, classic and minimalist interiors. These frames are the perfect gift, or you can use them to simply show off a favorite photo. 

♥ Features ♥
- Transparent 3 mm (1/8”) high quality acryl;
- Colors are double printed to ensure high color saturation and contrast;
- Mirror printing on the reverse side ensures a high-gloss look to the finished product;
- All frames come beautifully wrapped, making them the perfect present;
- Frame stand is included for FREE.

♥ Stands only ♥
Stands separately are available here:
https://www.etsy.com/shop/GoldenOwlDecor?section_id=32359621

♥ Add-on: Corner Holes ♥
Option to add 4 extra holes at the corners of the plaque/frame is available here:
https://www.etsy.com/listing/967444942/add-on-corner-holes-modern-music-plaque

♥ Add-on: Digital Version Only ♥
To get this personalized plaque or frame in digital form only (SVG + PNG), you have to order the Digital Version Only service. The link is provided below. You have to send us all personalization details, in the same was if you were ordering the physical version of the item. 
Note: Digital files are not included in the purchase of a physical version of the plaque.
https://www.etsy.com/listing/966010269/digital-version-only

♥ How to order ♥
1. Select the size and orientation of the frame you would like.
2. Select one of the available style options. All available styles are shown on the Styles Page in the Photos section. 
3. Please specify the color of the frame you would like. All available colors are shown in the color palette in the Photos section. 
4. Add your personal touches: Please clearly specify any frame text customizations that may be available in the frame design of your choice (maximum XX characters including spaces). 
5. Send us a message with your custom photo, after you order is finished. Custom photo must be a large image, minimum 1000 pixels wide. Small images may result in a blurry effect when it is printed. Images will be centered and may be partially cropped to fit photo rectangle. Additional color correction may be applied to create a better look.

♥ Processing and Shipping ♥
- Design and creation of custom frame requires one week (7 days).
- Currently, express shipping costs are very high, and I want this frame to be as affordable as possible for you. As a result, I ask you to be patient as shipment may take between two and three weeks (14 – 21 days) both for Europe and North America, though in many instances it has been faster.
- If delivery is urgent, I would not want you to be disappointed and I would recommend you look for a local supplier.
- After your frame has been shipped, I will mark your order as completed and you will get an Etsy email with tracking code. Additionally, you may find the tracking numbers under your existing orders.
- Please note that certain tracking systems take several days   to be updated, so do not worry if it appears nothing is happening.
- In the unlikely event your parcel has not arrived within 5 weeks, please contact me by email and will initiate an investigation with postal company. If the parcel has been lost in transit, I will resend a new plaque for you.
- We ensure that all frames are well wrapped to protect them against any damage. However, if your frame has been damaged in transit – send me a photo of the damage and I will send out a new frame to you.

♥ Add-on: Express Delivery ♥
Option to speedup delivery is available here:
https://www.etsy.com/listing/942819593/add-on-express-delivery-2-weeks-faster

♥ Returns Policy ♥
Because we custom create all orders, we do not accept returned items or exchanges. Cancellations are accepted within six (6) hours from the time your order is placed.
However, if you have any problems with your order or if we have made an error, we will be more than happy to assist you with resolving the issue.

If you have any questions, feel free to message me here on Etsy!
